<custom-nav-bar title="质保承诺" showBack="{{true}}" />
<view class="page-root merchant-warranty-style" style="{{pageRootStyle}}">
  <block wx:if="{{loading}}">
    <view class="warranty-style-loading"><text class="text-muted fs-body">加载中...</text></view>
  </block>
  <block wx:else>
    <view class="detail-section card">
      <text class="fs-body fw-medium">电子质保凭证（卡面样式）</text>
      <text class="text-muted fs-cap warranty-style-intro">
        分项质保由您向车主作出，以报价/方案中的「质保月数」为准。车主确认完工后，辙见将根据已确认方案固化电子凭证（含分项与存证防伪码）。此处仅选择卡面样式（默认应用于新完工单，单笔订单提交前也可更改）。
      </text>
    </view>
    <view class="detail-section card">
      <view class="section-title fs-body fw-medium warranty-style-section-title">选择默认样式</view>
      <view
        class="warranty-style-opt {{selectedId === item.id ? 'warranty-style-opt--on' : ''}}"
        wx:for="{{templates}}"
        wx:key="id"
        data-id="{{item.id}}"
        bindtap="onSelect"
      >
        <view class="warranty-style-opt-inner">
          <view class="warranty-style-opt-radio">{{selectedId === item.id ? '●' : '○'}}</view>
          <view class="warranty-style-opt-text">
            <text class="fs-body fw-medium">{{item.name}}</text>
            <text class="text-muted fs-cap">{{item.theme_label || '默认'}}主题</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="detail-section card warranty-style-preview-section" wx:if="{{previewCard}}">
      <view class="section-title fs-body fw-medium">完整卡面预览</view>
      <text class="text-muted fs-cap warranty-style-preview-hint">
        以下为示例维修厂名称（优先展示您店铺名）、示例订单、示例分项与示例防伪码，便于查看版式与纹样；正式凭证以实际订单与完工后存证为准。
      </text>
      <warranty-card-surface
        card="{{previewCard}}"
        themeClass="{{previewThemeClass}}"
        useSampleItems="{{true}}"
        showShareHint="{{false}}"
      />
    </view>
    <view class="safe-area-bottom" style="padding: var(--space-md);">
      <button class="btn-primary" loading="{{saving}}" disabled="{{saving}}" bindtap="onSave">保存为店铺默认</button>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
